description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces 2". The following 10 moving puzzles are included.
-Taketomi Island Village
-Kouri Beach
-Tomato clownfish in the sea at Aka Island
-Kabira Bay on Ishigaki Island
-Shisa and Cat
-Nirai Kanai Bridge
-Sea Anemone in the sea at Tokashiki Island
-Hibiscus Flowers
-Green sea turtle in the sea at Tokashiki Island
-Boraga Beach on Miyako Island
name: [Moving] Okinawa: Winds of the Ryukyu Islands
